title: Election Simulation
new-page: true
on-arrival: {!
// Reset everything
for (var p of Q.parties) {
    Q[p + '_parlament_s'] = 0;
    Q[p + '_parlament_pv'] = 0;
    for (var constituency of Q.parlament_constituencies) {
        for (var demographic of Q.parlament_demographics) {
            Q[p + '_parlament_' + constituency + '_' + demographic + '_support'] = 0;
        }
    }
}
for (var constituency of Q.congreso_constituencies) {
    for (var p of Q['congreso_parties_' + constituency]) {
        Q[p + '_congreso_s'] = 0;
        Q[p + '_congreso_pv'] = 0;
        if (constituency == 'catalunya') Q[p + '_congreso_pv_cat'] = 0;
        Q[p + '_congreso_' + constituency + '_support'] = 0;
    }
}

!}
set-jump: post_election_sim

The Election Simulation system is an in-game tool used for debugging and testing. Do play around with historic election results and see how the game handles them!

- @2012_11: Catalan Parlament (November 2012)
- @2015_9: Catalan Parlament (September 2015)
- @2015_12: Spanish Congreso (December 2015)
- @2016_6: Spanish Congreso (June 2016)
- @2019_4: Spanish Congreso (April 2019)
- @2019_11: Spanish Congreso (November 2019)
- @root: Back
# - @2017_12: Catalan Parlament (December 2017)

@2012_11
