{!<div style="width: 95%; justify-content: center; margin-top:-1em; display:flex;"><div class="box" style="width: 70%; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #ccc"><div class="box" style="display: inline-block; height: 1em; background-color: dimgrey; margin-right: 0.5em; border-radius: 3px; width:!}[+ congreso_participation_pc+]{!%;"></div></div></div>!}

Author's note: Congreso election simulations are more imperfect than Parlament ones, but the main goal of the in-game dynamic is to capture the general trends and the possible government formations, pacts, and deadlocks, which is mostly achieved.

**Government Formation**
# yeah this is hardcoded because its only the simulation scenes
[? if dl_congreso_showviz: No candidacy has been able to secure enough support to form a new government. New elections will happen in **June 2016**. ?]
[? if pdcat_congreso_showviz: <span style='color: #1d84ce;'>Mariano Rajoy</span> will lead a <span style='color: #1d84ce;'>PP minority government</span> with the assent of <span style='color: #f6c300; font-weight: bold;'>Cs</span>, <span style='color: #ffcc00; font-weight: bold;'>CC-PNC</span>, and the toleration of a broken <span style='color: #da291c; font-weight: bold;'>PSOE</span>.?]
[? if jxcat_congreso_showviz and fr_congreso_showviz: No candidacy has been able to secure enough support to form a new government. New elections will happen in **November 2019**. ?]
[? if jxcat_congreso_showviz and not fr_congreso_showviz: <span style='color: #da291c; font-weight: bold;'>Pedro Sánchez</span> will lead a <span style='color: #da291c; font-weight: bold;'>progressist</span> <span style='color: #5a205a; font-weight: bold;'>government</span> (<span style='color: #da291c; font-weight: bold;'>PSOE</span>-<span style='color: #5a205a; font-weight: bold;'>UP</span>) with the assent of <span style='color: #4aae4a; font-weight: bold;'>EAJ-PNV</span>, <span style='color: #027665; font-weight: bold;'>Más País</span>, <span style='color: #a2c7e4; font-weight: bold;'>BNG</span>, <span style='color: #ffcc00; font-weight: bold;'>CC-PNC</span>, <span style='color: #007351; font-weight: bold;'>¡TE!</span> and the toleration of <span style='color: #ff8000; font-weight: bold;'>ERC</span> and <span style='color: #00c19f; font-weight: bold;'>EH Bildu</span>. ?]

[? if not (dl_congreso_showviz or pdcat_congreso_showviz or jxcat_congreso_showviz): How did we get here??? ?]

